image_analysis.description: A photograph of a two-page spread from a book or report. The left page contains printed text, with the page number 150 at the bottom. The right page features four photographs related to Jeffrey Epstein, each with a caption. The photographs include an aerial view of a waterfront property, a group of three young women, a yearbook photo of a young man, and a photo of a young man on a beach. A document identifier is visible at the bottom right corner.
image_analysis.layout: Two-page spread. The left page is a single column of text. The right page has a multi-image layout with captions placed near the corresponding images.
